org.jruyi.workshop

Interface IWorkshopProfiler


  • public interface IWorkshopProfiler
    Service for profiling its bound workshop service.

    All statistics are effective only when profiling is started and will be dropped when profiling is stopped.

    Since:
    1.1
    See Also:
    IWorkshop
